            "category": "securities",
            "date": "2025-02-19",
            "headline": "Veeco to participate in Fireside Chat at Morgan Stanley conference in San Francisco on March 3, 2025.",
            "id": "8b13956e-d4ed-4f4b-a7ef-d0baec5ae00a",
            "is_major": false,
            "source": "GlobeNewswire",
            "source_type": "news",
            "summary": "Veeco Instruments Inc., a company listed on NASDAQ under the ticker symbol VECO, revealed that its management will take part in a Fireside Chat at the upcoming Morgan Stanley\u2019s Technology, Media, & Telecom Conference. The event is scheduled for March 3rd, 2025, at 6:20 PM ET, and will be held at the Palace Hotel in San Francisco, CA. Apart from the Fireside Chat, Veeco management will host in-person meetings with investors at the conference. Those interested in meeting with Veeco management during the event are advised to reach out to their Morgan Stanley contact to arrange a meeting time.",
            "tickers": [
                "NDXP",
                "VECO"
            ],
            "time": "23:22:13",
